                "STTA",
                "EDEG",
                "MOSEP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Energy Degradation in the Stack was Calculated",
                "According to C.F.Williamson Et Al., Cea-R3042(1966).",
                "Irradiations of a Few Minutes to Two Hours were Carried",
                "Out with Deuterons of Incident Energies of 50 and 90",
                "MeV, Respectively. Beam Currents Ranged Between 5 and",
                "10 Nanoampere."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Stack Consisting of Up to 40 Nabr-Pellets, Thickness",
                "Between 60 and 150 Mg/Cm**2, Encapsulated in",
                "Polyethylene Foils of 7 Mg/Cm**2. For Beam Monitoring,",
                "Al-Foils of 50 Micrometers were Inserted at Different",
                "Positions in the Stack. A Total of 5 Stacks were",
                "Irradiated."
              ]
            }
          ],
